<p class="review-lesson">[93] Light and joy and peace abide in me.</p>

<p><sup>2</sup> <em>I am the home of light and joy and peace.</em><br /> I welcome
them into the home I share<br /> With God because I am a part of Him.</p>

<p class="review-lesson">[94] I am as God created me.</p>

<p><sup>3</sup> <em>I will remain forever as I was</em>,<br /> Created by the
Changeless like Himself.<br /> And I am one with Him, and He with me.</p>

<p><sup>4</sup> On the hour:</p>

<p><sup>5</sup> <em>Light and joy and peace abide in me.</em></p>

<p><sup>6</sup> On the half hour:</p>

<p><sup>7</sup> <em>I am as God created me.</em></p>

